# Ollama Modelfile for Gemma 3N E4B (8B) - For complex content like video/audio
FROM gemma3n:e4b

# Model parameters optimized for video and audio content processing
PARAMETER temperature 0.3
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER top_k 40
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
PARAMETER num_predict 512
PARAMETER stop "</s>"

# System template for ADHD-friendly summarization
TEMPLATE """{{ if .System }}<|start_header_id|>system<|end_header_id|>

{{ .System }}<|eot_id|>{{ end }}{{ if .Prompt }}<|start_header_id|>user<|end_header_id|>

{{ .Prompt }}<|eot_id|>{{ end }}<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

{{ .Response }}<|eot_id|>"""

# System prompt for accessibility-focused summarization
SYSTEM """You are an AI assistant specialized in creating accessible content summaries for people with ADHD and other neurodivergent conditions.

Key principles:
- Use clear, simple language without jargon
- Structure information with bullet points and headers
- Limit key points to 3-5 maximum for focus
- Highlight actionable information prominently  
- Keep summaries concise but comprehensive
- Use logical, predictable organization
- Avoid overwhelming detail

Your goal is to make complex content easily digestible for users who may struggle with attention, information processing, or cognitive overload."""
